    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Before you begin...</strong></p><p>Get all your ingredients and equipment ready</p><p>Skim through these steps, then wash your fruit and veg</p><p>Note: Equipment and pan sizes vary. Make sure you cook food thoroughly (even if it takes you a little longer than 10 min)</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/re-nourish-roasted-carrot-and-ginger-soup-with-cheesy-curried-pittas/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/re-nourish-roasted-carrot-and-ginger-soup-with-cheesy-curried-pittas/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Trim, then slice your<strong> spring onion[s]</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/re-nourish-roasted-carrot-and-ginger-soup-with-cheesy-curried-pittas/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>grated cheese</strong> to a medium bowl with your <strong>mayo</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>curry powder </strong>and most of the <strong>sliced spring onion </strong>(save some for garnish!)</p><p>Give everything a good mix up until completely combined \u2013 this is your <strong>cheesy curried filling</strong></p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/re-nourish-roasted-carrot-and-ginger-soup-with-cheesy-curried-pittas/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Slice open the top of your <strong>sourdough pitta[s]</strong></p><p>Fill your <strong>sliced pitta </strong>with the <strong>cheesy curried filling</strong></p><p>Close the pitta and press down firmly \u2013 these are your <strong>cheesy curried pitta[s]</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/re-nourish-roasted-carrot-and-ginger-soup-with-cheesy-curried-pittas/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> cheesy curried pitta[s] </strong>and cover with a smaller pan</p><p>Add a heavy weight (e.g. several tins) to the top pan and cook for 3-4 min per side, checking occasionally or until the pitta is golden and the cheese has melted</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 5? Use 2 pans or you may need to do this in batches!</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/re-nourish-roasted-carrot-and-ginger-soup-with-cheesy-curried-pittas/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat your <strong>RE:NOURISH carrot soup </strong>according to the pack instructions</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/re-nourish-roasted-carrot-and-ginger-soup-with-cheesy-curried-pittas/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>RE:NOURISH carrot soup </strong>in bowls with the <strong>cheesy curried pitta[s] </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish the soup with the <strong>remaining sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
